data.description:
SPACIOUS 3 Bed 2 Bath HIDDEN GEM on 1 ACRE in the heart of Crestview with LOW COUNTY TAXES! TURN KEY HOME ready to go! This lush large 1 acre corner lot in Grandview Heights offers plenty of privacy with room for gardening, entertaining, RV charging, boat storage and more. As you approach the home, you are greeted by a massive covered front porch ready for your rocking chairs. As you enter the home, a small foyer opens up to the large living room with LVP flooring,  vaulted ceiling, dining area, and kitchen. These three spaces are all connected for that open concept feel. The kitchen has been remodeled, complete with SS appliances and a Z-line 6 burner gas stove, painted cabinetry with new hardware, new lighting, Corian counter tops, tile and shiplap backsplash under cabinet lighting, pantry and more. French doors in the living room lead you to the family room complete with brick gas/wood burning fireplace and door leading to the enclosed screen porch overlooking the beautiful backyard. To the left of the living room, you will find the large primary suite with sliding door leading to the enclosed screened in porch. The primary bathroom offers a double vanity, shower, water closet and massive closet. The home offers two additional exceptionally large bedrooms on the other side of the home, separated by a second full bathroom for guests.
The includes an indoor laundry room with pantry that connects to the oversized side entry garage with pull-down stairs, auto opener, and tub sink. This incredible lot has both spacious front and back yards for excellent curb appeal and maximum enjoyment for entertaining. The 1+ acre lot has many azaleas, a variety of Camellias, blueberry bushes, and mature trees throughout. The exterior of the home has a metal roof (screws and seals replaced in 2021), hurricane shutters, whole house generator, RV parking and charging, 12x24 workshop, and boat storage. HVAC replaced in 2018, Septic pumped in 2021, Termite bond in place. Grandview Heights offers some great amenities to include access to 4 lakes and a gated picnic area. Bring your plans and put your personal touch on this well loved home. Schedule your showing today!
